{"tid":1787409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「中大」段爺獲選為泰晤士高等教育年度人物","createTime":"2019-12-18T02:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T02:23:59.000Z","uid":184099,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e79244f47eee706be87b9e3bd32412f3d92d0ab3","tid":1787409,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:04:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中大校長段崇智，在上月中大反修例衝突中親自落場，在示威者和警方之間斡旋，此舉動令他獲英國泰晤士高等教育（Times Higher Education，THE）選為2019年高等教育界的年度人物。<br />\n<br />\nTHE今年共選出11名世界各地大學的領導者或學者為年度人物，大部分人來自歐洲、美國和澳洲學府，只有中大校長段崇智，是亞洲地區高等教育界的唯一獲選人物。</span></strong>THE讚揚他在上個月中大校園示威事件中的表現，指當本港所有大學高層正為示威情況所困之時，沒有人能像段崇智那般堅韌地為校園和學生站出來。THE形容段崇智到如「戰場」的示威現場斡旋，嘗試尋求和平解決的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1662484/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-%E6%AE%B5%E5%B4%87%E6%99%BA%E7%8D%B2%E9%81%B8%E7%82%BA%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1662484%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25B4%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2589%25A9&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BunqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=2acf6df5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1662484%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25B4%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%2599%25A4%2